  "detailed_description": "Search, search and search. Here's how you can find the answers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNightzoid is a horror game, combined with puzzle, that will make you extremely curious.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou enter a house to find out the mystery, but you have to avoid the \"Zoid\". To find out the mystery, you have to solve the puzzles and complete the endings.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSearch and read the letters to find out the story.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 10 Endings<br />\r\n- +200 achievements<br />\r\n- 13 letters<br />\r\n- 30 items<br />\r\n- many rooms and places to explore",
